    {
      "text": "Last edit about 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n29\nNeeds Review\n29\nJ-91 It progressively knew itself less + less falling into forgetfulness (of its own identity). viz: the very act of self-knowledge (\"anokhi.\" triggered off a vicious regress of progressively less + less self-knowledge - until, at the most debased + forgetful stage, it awakens itself to restored self-awareness (salvator salvandus) Each ring, emanation or level is an inferior copy of the one above it, with necessary loss of \"detail\" -",
